iblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1150</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; so <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">κ. κῶλα</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0011.tlg007.perseus-grc1:19\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ S.\">S.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ OC\">OC</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">19</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; then <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">κάμπτειν</foreign> alone, <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">sit down, rest</tr_>, ib.<bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0011.tlg007.perseus-grc1:85\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">85</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0006.tlg007.perseus-grc1:1080\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ E.\">E.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Hec.\">Hec.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1080</biblScope> </bibl>(lyr.); also <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">γόνυ κ</foreign>. <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">bend</tr_> the knee in worship, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0527.tlg048:45:23\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ LXX\">LXX</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Is.\">Is.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">45.23</biblScope></bibl>, etc.:—<gramGrp opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gramGrp\"> <gram type=\"voice\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gram\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Pass.\">Pass.</a></gram></gramGrp>, <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">bend oneself</tr_>, opp. <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἐκτείνεσθαι</foreign>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0059.tlg031:74b\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Pl.\">Pl.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Ti.\">Ti.</a></title_> <biblScop